Class Stream<A>

java.lang.Object
  fj.data.Stream<A>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<A>
public abstract class Stream<A>
extends Object
implements Iterable<A>

A lazy (not yet evaluated), immutable, singly linked list.
